          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Yiddish</add>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Yiddish</add>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <persName role="author">N. Ottinger</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Yiddish</add>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <sic>
                                                  <addressee>Rev. Isack Leeser</addressee>
                                        </sic>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Something is written with pencil sideways on the right
                                                  side of the page in Yiddish</add>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="3"/>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Yiddish</add>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>, Wed. day
                                        before</p>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <date>Rosh Hodesh Nissan (April)<lb/>1851</date>
                              </p>
                              <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>,
                                                  <placeName>Phila.</placeName></p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I hereby let you know that I<lb/> have sold the
                                        three prayer-books of<lb/> Ashkenazic &amp; Polish ritual,
                                        as well as the<lb/> three Pentateuchs. Please write to me
                                        what<lb/> to do with your money, and send me<lb/> again 6
                                        prayer-books of Ashkenazic<lb/> ritual. You might also send
                                        one set<lb/> holiday-books of Sephardic ritual with<lb/>
                                        translation, if that does not inconvenience<lb/> you too
                                        much and if they are not of<lb/> too high a price. Send them
                                        to me<lb/> at the lowest price.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">With respect, and wishes for a<lb/> happy holiday,
                                        Your friend,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName role="author">N. Ottinger</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>I should also like one prayer-book in<lb/> gilt binding, at lowest
                                        price.</p>
                    </body>
